      action: "Suppresses ovulation and HPO axis activity, reducing ovarian androgen production; provides regular progestin withdrawal to prevent endometrial hyperplasia; in endometriosis, suppresses cyclic endometrial implant stimulation and reduces peritoneal inflammation",
