        options: ["AUB-L (Leiomyoma); levonorgestrel IUD or combined OCPs","AUB-C (Coagulopathy); tranexamic acid","AUB-O (Ovulatory dysfunction); progesterone supplementation","AUB-E (Endometrial); endometrial ablation"],
